[[File:Fossil Island wyverns icon.png|left]]
'''Long-tailed Wyverns''' are [[Slayer monsters]] that require a [[Slayer]] level of 66 in order to be harmed. They reside in the [[Wyvern Cave]] on [[Fossil Island]]. Like with other [[Wyverns]], an [[elemental shield|elemental]], [[mind shield|mind]], [[dragonfire shield|dragonfire]] or [[ancient wyvern shield]] provides significant protection against their icy breath, and they are vulnerable to the effects of [[dragonbane weapons]]. These monsters require completion of the [[Bone Voyage]] quest to be assigned as a Slayer task.

